makeIfStmt

Stmt makeIfStmt(Exp cond,
                Stmt thenStmt,
                Stmt elseStmt)
make if statement. it's treat with 'and' 'or' like: 
    if EXP1 and EXP2
      T
    else
      F
    end

    =>
    IF EXP1
      IF EXP2
        T
      END
      goto ELSE_L
    ELSE
      ELSE_L:
      E
    END

    if EXP1 or EXP2
      T
    else
      E
    end

    =>
    IF EXP1
      THEN_L:
      T
    ELSE
      IF EXP2
        goto THEN_L
      END
      E
    END
